
Pseudo Code
-----------


three-query.php:

	connect to the database

	form query strings

	loop over queries

		do a query

		form a table header

		loop over rows

			print current row cell by cell

	close connection




query.php:

	get the query from JSON data

	check that "what" and "from" fields are provided

	validate the query data

	form the query string

	connect to the database

	send the query

	get the headers from the reply

	loop over rows

		pack the current row

		check if too many rows now

	close the access to the database

	return the response

